dc:description:
Front Row: Josh Trexler, Andy Potts, Michael O'Connor, Jr., Raymond Papa, Dino Dovellos, head coach Jon Urbanchek.

Second Row: Chris Thompson, Joe Palmer, John Reich, G.J. Zann, Francisco Suriano Siu.

Third Row: Scott Werner, manager Ben Jones, Michael McWha, Chris Laskowski, Jay Zawacki, David Stephens

Back Row: asst. coach Eric Namesnik, Steven Williams, Tom Malchow, Derya Buyukuncu, Brett Wilmot, Owen von Richter, Scott Meyer, Guillermo Ramis, Jeff Flermoen.

Not Pictured: Carlos Castillo, volunteer asst. coach Tim Chaix, diving coach Dick Kimball, student trainer John Schoenwetter, Nathan Shepard.
